    <h2>Overseas Study</h2>
    <p>Undergraduates majoring in Japanese Studies are encouraged to apply to various study programmes in Japan, including the NUS Student Exchange Programme and other prestigious programmes funded by the JCCI Foundation and the Monbukagakusho.  Department students have all demonstrated significant improvements in their Japanese competence after such long-term stays in Japan.  First-hand experience in the country also provides students with more direct insight and authentic knowledge on Japan.</p>
