    <h3>KYUSHU UNIVERSITY SUMMER PROGRAM</h3>
    <p>Kyushu University Summer Program - Asia in Today's World provides students with a unique opportunity to study Japanese language, culture and society.  Students will attend Japanese language classes and also courses on different aspects of Japan.  In addition, they also participate in study trips to places of cultural, social and historical interest and significance.  In order to provide a variety of living circumstances in Japan, two types of accommodation are arranged: off-campus accommodation and homestay.  This programme provides the students with a better knowledge of Japanese culture and lifestyle.</p>
    <p>Please refer to <a href="http://www.isc.kyushu-u.ac.jp/atw/index.htm">ATW website</a> for more information.</p>
